Constructs a new LinkCreatedAlert, initializing all mandatory fields.

Parameters:
feedIdentifier - The ItemIdentifier of the alert feed that generated this LinkCreatedAlert.
subjectIdentifier - The ItemIdentifier of the Item that is the subject of the alert feed that generated this LinkCreatedAlert.
alertType - A String containing the type of this LinkCreatedAlert, as returned by Alert.getAlertType().
timestamp - An PropertyValue containing the timestamp of this LinkCreatedAlert.
principalName - A String containing the name of the Principal whose actions triggered this LinkCreatedAlert.
linkIdentifier - The ItemIdentifier of the created Link.
linkedToEntityIdentifier - The ItemIdentifier of the Entity that was being monitored, to which the created Link was attached.
otherEntityIdentifier - The ItemIdentifier of the Entity at the opposite end of the created Link from the Entity that was being monitored.
